WN history \u2014 it is NOT a buy call."},"Ownership":{"verdict":"positive","score":1,"drivers":["+ DIIs accumulating (+7.25pp YoY)."],"rule":"Points: +1 promoter stake rising \u00b7 \u22121 promoter stake falling more than 1pp in a year \u00b7 \u22121 promoter pledge above 10% \u00b7 +1 for each of FII / DII accumulating (>0.5pp in a year). Verdict: positive at +1 or more, negative at \u22121 or less."}},"top_positives":["Trades above its 200-day average (+12%).","50-day average above the 200-day (golden cross).","High-quality business (81/100).","Conservatively financed (D/E 0.05\u00d7, interest cover 37.3\u00d7).","DIIs accumulating (+7.25pp YoY)."],"key_risks":["Lagging the NIFTY 500 by -12pp over 12 months.","In a deep drawdown (-40% from its peak)."],"monitor_next":["Next quarterly results (board-meeting date is an MVP-2 placeholder).","Re-rating toward / away from its median P/E (37.9\u00d7).","Relative-strength inflection vs its sector index.","Promoter pledge / institutional-holding changes next quarter."],"caveats":["corporate-action gaps, illiquid names, or a short listing history can distort returns/DMA/RS."],"confidence":"high","disclaimer":"Diagnostics only \u2014 a structured reading of price behaviour, business fundamentals, valuation and ownership for your OWN judgement. This is NOT a buy/sell/hold recommendation.","method":"Each dimension is a transparent points tally of the named signals listed beneath it \u2014 open a dimension to see the exact signals that fired and its rule. Verdict = positive at +2 or more / negative at \u22122 or less for Market, Business and Valuation; \u00b11 for Ownership. A 'positive' valuation means the multiple looks supportive vs the stock's OWN history \u2014 never a buy call."},"data_quality":{"price_asof":"2026-06-17","fundamentals_fetched":"2026-06-20","has_fundamentals":true,"has_shareholding":true,"liquidity_warning":null,"note":"Market data is daily and current; fundamentals & shareholding are as of the last cac